It can hear you anyway, right. And why would it care. Your eating. You do that every day. If whatever god realy does exist listend to every freakin one they couldn't be all powerful because their scedual is being controlled by people yapping thier mouths about why thier thankful to god because the people went out and got a job, and worked hard for the money.
